  <h1>Privacy Policy for SubAlert â€“ Subscription Reminder</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> July 2, 2025</p>
  <p><strong>Developer:</strong> [Your Full Name]</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>SubAlert does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data to the developer or any developer-controlled servers. All subscription data is stored only on your device and never sent elsewhere.</p>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
  <p>We use your locally stored data only to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Track subscription renewal dates</li>
    <li>Send reminders 3 days before billing</li>
    <li>Unlock premium features if purchased</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. In-App Purchases</h2>
  <p>Premium purchases are processed by Google Play. We do not handle or store your financial data. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google's Privacy Policy</a> for more.</p>

  <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>We may interact with services like:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Google Play Billing</li>
    <li>Push Notifications</li>
  </ul>
  <p>These services may collect technical data such as device type or IP address. Please review their respective privacy policies for full details.</p>

  <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>We do not store your data. If you uninstall the app, all local data is deleted automatically.</p>

  <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>Email: <a href="mailto:subalert.support@gmail.com">subalert.support@gmail.com</a></p>

  <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>This policy may be updated. We will notify users of major changes via the app and update the effective date at the top of this page.</p>

  <hr />
  <p><em>This app respects your privacy and keeps your data in your hands.</em></p>
